OL,3,CGreen light given to close two Wales
OL,4,CAir Ambulance bases after 2026
OL,6,FWelsh health boards have given the
OL,7,Fgreen light to close two Air Ambulance
OL,8,Fbases after 2026 following a vote on
OL,9,Fthe matter.
OL,11,FA meeting of the Welsh NHS' Joint
OL,12,FCommissioning Committee voted that the
OL,13,FWelshpool and Caernarfon bases will be
OL,14,Fclosed after 2026. The sites will be
OL,15,Fmerged into a new site in north Wales.
OL,17,FHowever, the decision hinges on
OL,18,Facceptable plans being developed for a
OL,19,Fbespoke car-based service in rural
OL,20,Fareas.
