OL,6,FA review proposed moving helicopters
OL,7,Ffrom Welshpool and Caernarfon to a new
OL,8,Fsite near the A55, rumoured to be in
OL,9,FDenbighshire.
OL,11,FThe charity has welcomed the move,
OL,12,Fwhich it says will "ensure as many
OL,13,Fpeople as possible" benefit and allow
OL,14,Fit to respond to 139 extra calls a
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FThe proposals to relocate their bases
OL,18,Fwent out to widespread consultation
OL,19,Fand were independently reviewed.
