OL,3,CGreen light given to close two Wales
OL,4,CAir Ambulance bases after 2026
OL,6,FThe Wales Ambulance Service says the
OL,7,Fbases in Caernarfon and Welshpool are
OL,8,Funderutilised. Thew new model would
OL,9,Fsee the current crews and existing
OL,10,Fassets at each of these bases come
OL,11,Ftogether in a new base located in the
OL,12,Fmiddle of north Wales.
OL,14,FOne crew will operate 8am until 8pm. A
OL,15,Fsecond crew will operate between 2pm
OL,16,Fand 2am.
OL,18,FWith existing bases in Cardiff and
OL,19,FLlanelli, it would mean the charity
OL,20,Fwould have three bases going forward.
