OL,6,FThere had been fears that aircraft
OL,7,Fwould be removed from the charity's
OL,8,Ffleet.
OL,10,FBut Chief Executive Dr Sue Barnes
OL,11,Faddressed these rumours: "The service
OL,12,Fwill continue to be delivered with
OL,13,Ffour helicopters and a fleet of rapid
OL,14,Fresponse vehicles."
OL,16,F"This is an improvement for all parts
OL,17,Fof Wales, particularly mid and north
OL,18,FWales who will be gaining a more local
OL,19,Fovernight service ` something they
OL,20,Fdon't have at present.
