OL,6,F"To put that into context, that is
OL,7,F750,000 people who have to rely on an
OL,8,Favailable response from Cardiff after
OL,9,Fthe hours of 8pm. This solution allows
OL,10,Fus to remedy that at no extra cost to
OL,11,Fthe people of Wales."
OL,13,FHowever, Dr Barnes added that the
OL,14,Fcharity empathised with "genuine
OL,15,Fconcern and anxieties" about care
OL,16,Fprovision and that this has been
OL,17,Fraised with the Chief Ambulance
OL,18,FServices Commissioner.
